## Coordination Workflows

### Check for Package Updates

```bash
for pkg in extended-data-types lifecyclelogging vendor-connectors; do
  echo "=== $pkg ==="
  GH_TOKEN="$GITHUB_JBCOM_TOKEN" gh release list --repo jbcom/$pkg --limit 3
done
```

